title: INXS - Kick (1987) Flac[24Bit 96KHz Vinyl]
description:
=================================

Kick is the sixth studio album by the Australian rock band INXS, released in 1987 by WEA in Australia,
 Atlantic Records in the United States and Phonogram Records in the United Kingdom on Audio CD, Compact Cassette 
and Gramophone record. As the band's most successful studio album, it is certified six times platinum by the RIAA, 
and spawned four US top 10 singles, "New Sensation", "Never Tear Us Apart", "Devil Inside" and "Need You Tonight", 
the last of which reached the top of the Billboard singles charts. At the 1988 MTV Video Music Awards, the band took
 home five Moonmen for the "Need You Tonight"/"Mediate" video.

The album was produced by Chris Thomas and recorded by David Nicholas in Sydney, Australia and in Paris. The album
 was mixed by Bob Clearmountain at Air Studios in London.
